## Dependencies and Installation Intructions:

Get ssparse
    
    git clone https://github.com/nefan/ssparse.git

Download and install SuiteSparse_config and CXSparse from
http://www.suitesparse.com

Download and install CUDA 5.0 (or above) if you wish to use CUDA.

cd to the ssparse directory and edit options in ssparse_config.mk
Installation directory, compiler flags etc. are obtained from the SuiteSparse
config.

Then compile and install

    make
    make install
